## Agent YAML Frontmatter Spec

Each agent in `.claude/agents/` gets YAML frontmatter:

```yaml
---
name: agent-name
description: When/why to use this agent
tools: [relevant tools]
model: sonnet
maxTurns: N
permissionMode: acceptEdits
memory: project
skills:
  - skill-name (if applicable)
---
```

### Agent Configuration Table

| Agent | name | tools | maxTurns | skills |
|-------|------|-------|----------|--------|
| PM Coordinator | `pm-coordinator` | WebFetch, Read, Write, Edit, Bash, Task | 30 | `project-research`, `roadmap-manager` |
| Backend Architect | `backend-architect` | Read, Write, Edit, Bash | 20 | — |
| Frontend Dev | `frontend-dev` | Read, Write, Edit, Bash | 20 | — |
| Python Pro | `python-pro` | Read, Write, Edit, Bash | 15 | — |
| Competitive Intel | `competitive-intel` | WebFetch, WebSearch, Read, Write, Edit, Bash | 25 | — |
| Doc Crawler | `doc-crawler` | WebFetch, Read, Write, Bash | 30 | — |
| Doc Auditor | `doc-auditor` | Read, Write, Edit, Bash, Grep, Glob | 20 | — |

